":175.22,"text":"And it goes something like this.","duration":4.55,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.16166666666666663,0.1977469649878302,0.0,0.0375,0.24000000000000002,0.13599999999999998,0.17890109890109868,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.3291204474817453,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.35076923076923017,0.1,0.8065,0.3236703296703296],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":175.22,"end":184.86,"text":"No greater love has someone than that person will lay down their life for their friends.","duration":9.64,"vector":[0.24253562503633297,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.14968749999999997,0.06,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.13240624999999998,0.2044813278008297,0.6212678125181665,0.0,0.25402850002906635,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.24253562503633297,0.5,0.41045643153526923,0.1,0.9664999999999999,0.4283586483547821],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":184.86,"end":197.88,"text":"So that always struck me is a very strong expression of how important friendship can be and should be.","duration":13.02,"vector":[0.4472135954999579,0.3341640786499874,0.37860679774997896,0.16078947368421054,0.15051264504817743,0.11065789473684212,0.0375,0.19573684210526318,0.13573684210526316,0.24311263606829003,0.6118033988749895,0.165939849254992,0.19416407864998736,0.1,0.027016261237511552,0.0,0.0625,0.30000000000000004,0.0,0.5452563225240887,0.37537634408602183,0.1,0.9175685364886239,0.38989121834798257],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":197.88,"end":205.65,"text":"And what a responsibility friendship actually is.","duration":7.77,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.28964285714285715,0.32116516898883724,0.21892857142857144,0.0375,0.1524285714285714,0.17439285714285713,0.1475675675675675,0.5,0.23940140490643416,0.06,0.7093853943072869,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.27765765765765743,0.1,0.8265,0.31427027027027027],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":205.65,"end":214.22,"text":"A good friend of course often becomes equivalent to a family member.","duration":8.57,"vector":[0.2773500981126146,0.03358994113243127,0.08000000000000002,0.21583333333333338,0.16753353277006305,0.18083333333333335,0.0375,0.16766666666666669,0.15225,0.11845347937012544,0.1767095663283081,0.0,0.28188007849009167,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.3650408401400235,0.1,0.9265000000000001,0.24087795707669926],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":214.22,"end":224.22,"text":"The the those members of your family who are not blood relations, but are related to you.","duration":10.0,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.15823529411764709,0.28222222222222226,0.11808823529411766,0.0375,0.19276470588235295,0.13497058823529412,0.20750000000000002,0.5,0.17308271040406537,0.06,0.1,0.2796362432175337,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.4175,0.5110397244812026,0.934832738110422,0.3063227513564933],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":224.22,"end":236.7,"text":"And some other way, of course there is relation by marriage, but often people become family members simply by being sincere and genuine friends.","duration":12.48,"vector":[0.2,0.0,0.08000000000000002,0.19395833333333334,0.06,0.04083333333333334,0.0375,0.22366666666666668,0.1456875,0.14423076923076936,0.304,0.0,0.12,0.1,0.26,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5827837796876729,0.4565384615384618,0.1,0.7966,0.2520692307692308],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":236.7,"end":243.93,"text":"And certainly in my life friendship has been extraordinarily important to me.","duration":7.23,"vector":[0.2773500981126146,0.2,0.5881193288818454,0.24395833333333333,0.16753353277006305,0.18083333333333335,0.0375,0.16766666666666669,0.16068749999999998,0.20448132780082956,0.6386750490563073,0.0,0.14320502943378438,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.5076923076923077,0.0,0.39246646722993694,0.41045643153526895,0.1,0.9265000000000001,0.3590794081515104],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":243.93,"end":253.93,"text":"Most saliently because of the fact that I have traveled so much and I have spent so much time going from one place to another.","duration":10.0,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.29344268295370746,0.139,0.06,0.0955,0.0375,0.2018,0.25144276780623,0.2675,0.5980580675690921,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.042136125673998756,0.0,0.0625,0.4322926079014275,0.0,0.41850482146251333,0.5575,0.1,0.7962077486893402,0.39143438837901867],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":253.93,"end":270.09,"text":"And I'm really relying on the good wishes of others and I have been extremely fortunate to have in many different countries met many different people who I can honestly say have become.","duration":16.16,"vector":[0.17149858514250882,0.2,0.2123529411764706,0.18325757575757579,0.20640627247290513,0.05517412153435589,0.0375,0.21793035138625766,0.14247727272727273,0.2331559405940597,0.5,0.13420574976682972,0.11144957554275264,0.27080731788505596,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.5822688904063047,0.0,0.5,0.47736386138613923,0.1,0.6265,0.33994678217821794],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":270.09,"end":275.09,"text":"Good friends and many of them have become very much like family.","duration":5.0,"vector":[0.2773500981126146,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.1408333333333333,0.16753353277006305,0.0,0.0375,0.24000000000000002,0.12974999999999998,0.26,0.5,0.0,0.14320502943378438,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.2838002991550946,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.54,0.1,0.9265000000000001,0.348],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":275.09,"end":303.18,"text":"So the there is definitely a concept that when someone is a true and genuine friend that there is a connection created that is something beyond the ordinary connections that we make and every everyday interaction with one another in the context of the world.","duration":28.09,"vector":[0.29488391230979427,0.2884651736929383,0.15372097807744858,0.2634212269064033,0.2223409956606085,0.15861111111111112,0.0375,0.17655555555555555,0.16652636807192098,0.2355355888790976,0.6474419561548972,0.11892127500773172,0.22218615177038686,0.1,0.06890692411480656,0.10811025000702883,0.0625,0.2589767824619589,0.0,0.5648661500042172,0.40034887860448526,0.16486615000421728,0.3937983768296674,0.3863676830717474],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":303.18,"end":315.18,"text":"And this is something that is strongly reflected in our Indo European languages, particularly in Indo Iranian.","duration":12.0,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.2707352941176471,0.23774208446282352,0.22397058823529412,0.0375,0.15041176470588236,0.16872058823529412,0.18625000000000003,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.36791666666666667,0.1944087511294902,0.9465000000000001,0.325875],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":315.18,"end":325.18,"text":"The word for friend in Sanskrit is mithra that appears in ancient Iranian, avastas, mithra.","duration":10.0,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.0,0.21750000000000003,0.15896309330796704,0.16750000000000004,0.0375,0.173,0.15275,0.1925,0.225,0.0,0.185,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.38249999999999995,0.1,0.9864999999999999,0.27275000000000005],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":325.18,"end":335.44,"text":"And both that word, mithra and Sanskrit appears to emerge from the root MITH.","duration":10.26,"vector":[0.0,0.275,0.0,0.26256527018457876,0.06,0.10464285714285716,0.0375,0.19814285714285715,0.16626958105537362,0.2573391812865498,0.21090055512641945,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.21482669175962224,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.35879142300194955,0.1,0.9664999999999999,0.28938186541124883],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":335.44,"end":342.86,"text":"And mith means literally to unite to pair up to couple.","duration":7.42,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.1415909090909091,0.06,0.0,0.0375,0.24000000000000002,0.12997727272727272,0.19118598382749302,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.3794339622641504,0.1,0.9065000000000001,0.3273557951482479],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":342.86,"end":347.95,"text":"And from it we get the Sanskrit word mithuna.","duration":5.09,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.14916666666666667,0.3294321511660492,0.11416666666666665,0.0375,0.19433333333333336,0.13224999999999998,0.21261296660117943,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.429430255402752,0.2194321511660492,0.8665,0.3337838899803538],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":347.95,"end":353.95,"text":"And mithuna means twins like Gemini, the twins astrological twins.","duration":6.0,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.26375,0.17496461272068817,0.07181989494000637,0.0375,0.21127204202399746,0.16662499999999997,0.20500000000000002,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.29494691908103227,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.4116666666666667,0.1,0.8865000000000001,0.3315],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":353.95,"end":357.08,"text":"And mithuna means a couple.","duration":3.13,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.1725,0.06,0.12749999999999997,0.0375,0.18900000000000003,0.13924999999999998,0.19980830670926536,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.3995527156549525,0.1,0.7865,0.3299424920127796],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Friendships and Runanubandh with Robert Svoboda _ Living with Reality __watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":357.08,"end":367.5,"text":"And mithuna or my tuna also means copulation when two people come together and unite physically that is also a coupling.","duration":10.42,"vector":[0.21320071